{"tid":1756711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官准記協介入覆核選民冊禁令","createTime":"2019-11-26T07:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:07:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a99d8ec35c03ae3609a8162c0686eb4a05ce230","tid":1756711,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/XPQYJZPYMSQQ777XKBJZO5MY6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FXPQYJZPYMSQQ777XKBJZO5MY6Y%2F&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV05Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=4d0f5125\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FXPQYJZPYMSQQ777XKBJZO5MY6Y%2F&h=fdddaafc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/XPQYJZPYMSQQ777XKBJZO5MY6Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n官准記協介入覆核選民冊禁令<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191126/large/1574698536_7a84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574698536_7a84.jpg&h=8db0d67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察員佐級協會針對選民登記冊的司法覆核案12月16日審理。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港警察隊員佐級協會指區議會選民登記冊洩露私隱，擔心助長對警察「起底」，故申請司法覆核，並取得臨時禁制令，限制登記冊不能結合展示選民姓名和住址。香港記者協會憂慮案件損害新聞自由，令傳媒難以偵查種票，故申請介入案件向法庭提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：校方今派人入校園尋留守者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件下月審理<br />\n<br />\n高等法院昨聆訊，記協的申請沒受反對，法官批准介入。案件12月16日審理，預留兩天。<br />\n<br />\n案件建議答辯人包括選管會、總選舉主任及選舉登記主任，由法官周家明審理，將採用合併覆核許可及正審的方式聆訊，議題之一是法例是否容許選民姓名和住址分開展示。<br />\n<br />\n周家明法官早前拒絕應員佐級協會申請頒發臨時禁制令，認為未必能防止起底。及後上訴庭指周官衡量私隱權的標準出錯，認為向公眾結合公開選民姓名和住址，的確會增加起底風險，而起底會危害整個社會，因此頒下臨時禁制令。禁制令限制答辯人不能結合公開選民姓名和住址，直至本案有判決，但候選人獲取的登記冊不受限制。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL3042/19<br />\n■記者勞東來"},{"pid":"643e747cba1eea0670f6de2b455d1e444968ef4d","tid":1756711,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線勿鬆懈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV05Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=1e1aa1f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"}]}